<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>@ViewData["Title"]</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/js/all.min.js"></script>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            margin-top: 60px;
        }

        .navbar {
            background-color: #007bff;
            font-weight: bold;
            padding: 15px 0;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #ffbf00;
            position: fixed;
            width: 100%;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000; 
        }

        .navbar-nav .nav-link {
            color: white !important;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            padding: 10px 20px;
        }

        .navbar-brand {
            color: white;
            font-size: 1.75rem;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .navbar-nav .nav-link:hover {
            color: #ffbf00 !important;
        }

        .hero-section {
            background-image: url('https://via.placeholder.com/1920x1080');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            padding: 100px 0;
            text-align: center;
            color: black;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #007bff;
        }

            .hero-section h2 {
                font-size: 3rem;
                font-weight: bold;
                color: #007bff; 
                text-shadow: 2px 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
            }

            .hero-section p {
                font-size: 1.25rem;
                font-weight: bold;
                text-shadow: 2px 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
                background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6); 
                padding: 10px 20px;
                border-radius: 8px;
            }

        .card {
            border-radius: 10px;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease-in-out;
            background: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

            .card:hover {
                transform: scale(1.05);
            }

        .card-body {
            padding: 40px;
        }

        .card-title {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
        }

        .card-text {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #555;
        }

        .section-title {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: #007bff;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 40px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
        }

        .footer {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #777;
        }

        .sidebar {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 250px;
            height: 100vh;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 30px;
            border-right: 2px solid #007bff;
        }

            .sidebar a {
                display: block;
                text-decoration: none;
                color: #007bff;
                padding: 10px 0;
                font-weight: bold;
            }

                .sidebar a:hover {
                    color: #ffbf00;
                }

        .content {
            margin-left: 270px;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .new-section {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 60px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

            .new-section h2 {
                font-size: 2rem;
                color: #007bff;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }

            .new-section p {
                font-size: 1.25rem;
                color: #555;
            }

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Navigation Bar -->
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light fixed-top">
        <div class="container">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="#">Hospital Appointment System</a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav" aria-controls="navbarNav" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
                <ul class="navbar-nav ms-auto">
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="#aboutUs">About Us</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="#experience">Experience</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="@Url.Action("Index", "Patients")">Manage Patients</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="@Url.Action("Index", "Doctors")">Manage Doctors</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="@Url.Action("Index", "Appointments")">Appointments</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    
    <div class="sidebar">
        <h4>Dashboard</h4><br />
        <a href="@Url.Action("Index", "Appointments")">Book Appointment</a>
        <a href="@Url.Action("Index", "Appointments")">View Appointments</a>
        <a href="@Url.Action("Index", "Doctors")">Manage Doctors</a>
        <a href="@Url.Action("Index", "Patients")">Manage Patients</a>
    </div>


    <div class="content">
        
        <div class="hero-section">
            <h2>Welcome to Our Hospital Appointment System</h2>
            <p>Book, view, and manage your appointments effortlessly with our user-friendly platform.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="new-section">
            <h2>Our Commitment to Quality Healthcare</h2>
            <p>Our platform ensures that your healthcare experience is seamless and hassle-free, with a focus on convenience and reliability.</p>
        </div>

        
        <div id="aboutUs" class="container">
            <h1 class="section-title">About Us</h1>
            <p>Our Hospital Appointment System was created with the patient in mind. Our goal is to make healthcare more accessible and efficient by allowing patients to book and manage their appointments online.We understand that scheduling medical visits can be time-consuming and stressful, so we have developed a seamless platform that simplifies the process.</p>
        </div>

        <div id="experience" class="container mt-5">
            <h1 class="section-title">Our Experience</h1>
            <p>
                With over a decade of expertise in healthcare management and IT solutions, we have empowered countless healthcare providers to streamline their operations, enhance patient care, and optimize efficiency. Our commitment to innovation and excellence ensures that medical professionals can focus on what truly matters—delivering quality healthcare.







            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

  
    <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; 2025 Hospital Appointment System | All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
